data.description: OPEN HOUSE 12/17/23 10 AM TO 4 PM. $115,000.00 PRICE REDUCTION! With Large down payment the Seller Will Finance at 4.5% FIXED. $1400/MO P&I PAYMENT! Save $150,000.00 in interest & loan fees! Room for 15 Horses, Sheep, Goats & Chickens perfect for this ranch. 344,560 sq ft (7.91 Acres) horse ranch with plentiful water. Two horse structures to provide shade for your horses and a wash rack with plenty of horse fencing. Also your own ZIP LINE.  Perimeter has beautiful vinyl fencing. Hay Barn that can accommodate a hay squeeze. 6 different storage sheds. Electric hookups for 8 RV's. Power in several of the out buildings including 110A, 220A, and 440AMPS. 75% OF THE PROPERTY IS FLAT IN THE 4 HORSE PASTURES. Property goes up the hillside which gives you a view to see the city lights down in the valley at night & the constellations above look like you can reach out & touch the stars as you sit in your back yard or even from your DR, LR or Master Suite. 2 Fabulous Custom Solar Powered Wrought Iron Gates that open with the clicker in your vehicle or with the electronic keypad outside the Gates or from inside your home you can buzz them in if you desire. This is a single level 23 year old stucco home with an attached 2 car garage. Fabulous efficient wood burning stove keeps the house comfy plus paid for solar screens keep it COOL. Adjacent to Rd 416 so a commuter can get to Fresno, Madera, Merced or Yosemite. No HOA FEES! 10 outbuildings on the property!
